sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant API Server
    participant Project Controller
    participant cert-manager

    User->>API Server: Create Project (cluster-scoped)
    API Server-->>User: Confirm creation

    Project Controller->>API Server: Watch Project
    API Server-->>Project Controller: Notify Project creation

    Project Controller->>API Server: Create Namespace (named after Project)
    Note over Project Controller: Namespace name = Project name

    alt CA enabled
        Project Controller->>API Server: Create Issuer (SelfSigned)
        API Server->>cert-manager: Issuer created

        Project Controller->>API Server: Create Certificate
        Note over Project Controller: Certificate uses Issuer<br/>SecretName: ca.secretName<br/>IsCA: true
        API Server->>cert-manager: Certificate created
    end

    Project Controller->>API Server: Create ServiceAccount
    Note over Project Controller: Name: {project-name}-serviceaccount

    Project Controller->>API Server: Create Role
    Note over Project Controller: Permissions for:<br/>- pods (get, list)<br/>- secrets (get, list, create, patch)<br/>- configmaps (create, get, list, patch, update)<br/>- units (get, list)<br/>- redisreplications (get, list, patch, update)<br/>- events (create, patch)

    Project Controller->>API Server: Create RoleBinding
    Note over Project Controller: Binds Role to ServiceAccount

    Project Controller->>API Server: Create Secret (AES key)
    Note over Project Controller: 32-char hex key for encryption<br/>Stored in project annotation for self-heal

    Project Controller->>Project Controller: Update Project annotation
    Note over Project Controller: Store AES key in Project annotation
